title: Shounen Ai no Bigaku #1-#13_#15-#17
description:
Shounen Ai no Bigaku #1 through 13 and 15 through #17, all clumped together for your enjoyment. Regrettably, none of it is translated...but it&#039;s still good. Please, after you finish this torrent, leave it open and seed for a while...it&#039;s rather huge. ^_^

Bear in mind also that this is all shotacon with josou shounen tossed in as well here and there. It&#039;s not everyone&#039;s cup of tea as far as hentai doujinshi goes.
